    "John Trapp": "Of the of Kohath `[char_Kohath_Gen_46]`. ] Kohath `[char_Kohath_Gen_46]` was not Levi\u2019s firstborn, but Gershom: and yet he hath the pre-eminence, and chief charge, as of the ark, tables, candlestick, altars, &amp;c., { #Nu 3:31 } perhaps because Moses `[char_Moses_Exo_2]` and Aaron `[char_Aaron_Exo_6]` were of that family.\nVer.\n2. Of the of Kohath.] Kohath was not Levi\u2019s firstborn, but Gershom: and yet he hath the pre-eminence, and chief charge, as of [v_Num_3_31] the ark, tables, candlestick, altars, &c., {#Nu 3:31} perhaps because Moses `[char_Moses_Exo_2]` and Aaron `[char_Aaron_Exo_6]` were of that family.\nVer.",
